codeometer (1.2.0) stable; urgency=low

  * Major code restructuring and new features
  * Split code into modular components
  * Added comment line counting (--comments)
  * Added hidden file support (--hidden)
  * Added help and version commands
  * Improved project type detection
  * Enhanced statistics and reporting
  * Added progress bar for large projects
  * Fixed various bugs and improved error handling

